function Start()
	T_MONSTERS = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "MONSTERS")
	idCorpse = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "CORPSE")[1]
	T_GORE = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "GORE")

	-- Spawn
	for i, idMonster in ipairs(T_MONSTERS) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMonster) then
			Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idMonster, false)
		end
	end
	
	--Pauses to give time for spawners to line up with blood splat
	--Hydra.Wait(0.375)
	
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idCorpse, S_PWR_BURST)
	
	for i, idGore in ipairs(T_GORE) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idGore) then
			Hydra.ActorEnable(idGore)
		end
	end
end

unk_993f312.value:
T_MONSTERS = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "MONSTERS")
idCorpse = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "CORPSE")[1]

-- Initial Setup
for i, idMonster in ipairs(T_MONSTERS) do
	--Playing dead
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idMonster, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idMonster, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(idMonster, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(idMonster, S_ANIM_DEAD)
end
